trans-unit.source: Provides design-time support in a visual designer for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref> Web server control.
trans-unit.target: Gir støtte for utforming i en visuelle utformeren for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref> Web serverkontroll.

trans-unit.source: In a visual designer, when you switch from Source to Design view, the markup source code that describes the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control is parsed and a design-time version of the control is created on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: I en visuelle utformeren når du bytter fra kilden til utformingsvisning markup kildekode som beskriver den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontrollen analyseres og en utformingen versjon av kontrollen er opprettet på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>

trans-unit.source: When you switch back to Source view, the design-time control is persisted to the markup source code and edited into the markup for the Web page.
trans-unit.target: Når du går tilbake til visning i datakilden, er utformingen kontrollen beholdt i markup kildekode og redigeres i markup for websiden.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner> class when it creates the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control or a copy of that control on the design surface.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner>klasse når det oppretter den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontroll eller en kopi av kontrollen på utformingsoverflaten.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner>

trans-unit.source: Gets the action list collection for this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter handlingen liste-samlingen for utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The ActionLists property creates a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> object for the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner> object, adds the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> object to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> object obtained from the base property, and then returns this collection.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen ActionLists oppretter en <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekt den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner>objekt, legger til den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>objekt i <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>objektet hentet fra egenskapen basis, og returnerer deretter denne samlingen.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"></xref> associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection"> </xref> tilknyttet utformeren.

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner"></xref> control allows resizing.
trans-unit.target: Angir om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner"> </xref> kontrollen kan endre størrelse.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control allows resizing; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kontrollen tillater endring; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of automatic format schemes that will be displayed in the **Auto Format** dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av automatisk formatering-skjemaene som skal vises i den **automatisk Format** dialogboksen.

trans-unit.source: The elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection> object are derived from the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat> class and are populated from internally defined XML-encoded constant strings.
trans-unit.target: Elementene i den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>objektet er avledet fra den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat>klasse og fylles ut fra internt definerte XML-kodet konstant strenger.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormat> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"></xref> that contains the predefined schemes for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerAutoFormatCollection"> </xref> som inneholder de forhåndsdefinerte skjemaene for den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to render the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method sets the mode of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control, which can be a copy, to the current mode of the actual control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetDesignTimeHtml angir modus for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontroll, som kan være en kopi, til gjeldende modus for faktiske kontrollen.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>

trans-unit.source: Next, it forces the child controls to be recreated, and then calls the base method to generate the markup.
trans-unit.target: Neste den tvinger underordnede kontroller opprettes, og kaller deretter metoden base for å generere koden.

trans-unit.source: If an error occurs, the GetDesignTimeHtml calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A> method to generate the markup for a placeholder.
trans-unit.target: Hvis det oppstår feilen, GetDesignTimeHtml kall av <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A>metode for å generere koden for en plassholder.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner.GetErrorDesignTimeHtml%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the markup used to render the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref> at design time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder markup brukes til å gjengi den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref> under utformingen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that is used to render the associated control at design time and populates a collection of designer regions.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som brukes til å gjengi den tilknyttede kontrollen på utformingstidspunktet og fyller ut en samling av designer områder.

trans-unit.source: The GetDesignTimeHtml method calls the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml> method to generate the markup for the design-time rendering of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control.
trans-unit.target: Metodekall GetDesignTimeHtml den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml>metode for å generere markup utformingen gjengivelse av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml>

trans-unit.source: It also adds a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion> object to the `regions` parameter that describes the current view of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control.
trans-unit.target: Det også legger til en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion>objekt i `regions` som beskriver gjeldende visning av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegion>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"></xref> to which a definition of the current view of the associated control has been added.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.DesignerRegionCollection"> </xref> til som en definisjon av gjeldende visning av den tilknyttede kontrollen er lagt til.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the markup used to render the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref> at design time.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder markup brukes til å gjengi den <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref> under utformingen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the persisted form of the current template of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Henter faste skjemaet for gjeldende mal for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The GetEditableDesignerRegionContent method serializes the current template (the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.ChangePasswordTemplate%2A> or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.SuccessTemplate%2A> property) of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control to its persisted form, which is a <xref:System.String> object of markup text.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEditableDesignerRegionContent serializes gjeldende mal (den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.ChangePasswordTemplate%2A>eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.SuccessTemplate%2A>egenskapen) for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontrollen det faste skjemaet, som er en <xref:System.String>objekt av markeringstekst.</xref:System.String> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.SuccessTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.ChangePasswordTemplate%2A>

trans-unit.source: This persisted form consists of the serialized child controls appended together.
trans-unit.target: Dette faste skjemaet består av de serialiserte underordnede kontrollene føyes sammen.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> that is not used by this GetEditableDesignerRegionContent override.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> som ikke brukes av denne GetEditableDesignerRegionContent overstyringen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing the persisted form of the current template of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder faste skjemaet for gjeldende mal for den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref>.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets the markup that renders to a placeholder containing information about the error that occurred while attempting to create or render the associated control at design time.
trans-unit.target: Henter markup som gjengir på en plassholder som inneholder informasjon om feilen som oppstod under forsøk på å opprette eller gjengi den tilknyttede kontrollen under utformingen.

trans-unit.source: The placeholder contains the type and control names, an error message, and the <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A> property that is associated with the `e` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Plassholderen inneholder type og kontroll navnene, en feilmelding og <xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>-egenskap som er knyttet til den `e` parameteren.</xref:System.Exception.Message%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Exception> that was thrown while creating or rendering the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Exception>som oppstod under oppretting eller gjengivelse av den tilknyttede kontrollen.</xref:System.Exception>

trans-unit.source: The markup for the placeholder that contains information about the specified exception.
trans-unit.target: Markup for plassholderen som inneholder informasjon om det angitte unntaket.

trans-unit.source: Prepares the designer to view, edit, and design the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Forbereder utformeren for å vise, redigere og utforme den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The designer host calls the Initialize method when it is ready to use the designer to render the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control.
trans-unit.target: Spørringsutformer verten kaller i initialiseringsmetoden når den er klar til å bruke designer til å gjengi den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>

trans-unit.source: The Initialize method and its base methods configure properties and connect events that are necessary for the operation of the designer.
trans-unit.target: I initialiseringsmetoden base metodene konfigurere egenskaper og koble hendelser som er nødvendige for operasjonen av designer.

trans-unit.source: The `component` parameter is the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control that is associated with this designer, or a copy of the control specified by `component`.
trans-unit.target: Den `component` parameteren er av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontrollen som er tilknyttet utformeren eller en kopi av kontrollen som er angitt av `component`.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref>, which implements <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref>, som implementerer <xref href="System.ComponentModel.IComponent"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Used by the designer to remove or add additional properties for display in the **Properties** grid or to shadow properties of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Brukes av designer for å fjerne eller legge til flere egenskaper for visning i den **Egenskaper** rutenett eller skyggen egenskapene for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: Control designers use methods derived from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to shadow various control properties with corresponding design-time properties that the designer implements, and to add or remove properties from the **Properties** grid.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen utviklere bruker metodene som er avledet fra den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoden skyggelegge ulike egenskaper for kontroll med tilsvarende utformingen egenskaper som designer implementerer, og du kan legge til eller Fjern egenskaper fra den **Egenskaper** rutenett.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.ComponentDesigner.PreFilterProperties%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control, the PreFilterProperties method sets the <xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute.Browsable%2A> attribute to `false` for properties that do not apply to templates (removes them from the **Properties** grid) when a user template has been defined.
trans-unit.target: For den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontrollerer PreFilterProperties metoden angir den <xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute.Browsable%2A>attributt til `false` for egenskaper som ikke gjelder for maler (fjerner dem fra den **Egenskaper** rutenett) når en brukermal er definert.</xref:System.ComponentModel.BrowsableAttribute.Browsable%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>

trans-unit.source: A collection implementing the <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary> of the added and shadowed properties.
trans-unit.target: En samling implementering av <xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>av egenskapene tillagt og skyggelagt.</xref:System.Collections.IDictionary>

trans-unit.source: Specifies whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner"></xref> control uses an outer table container to apply inline CSS style rules.
trans-unit.target: Angir om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner"> </xref> kontroll bruker et ytre tabell-beholder til å bruke innebygd CSS-stilregler.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner> control uses an outer table container to apply inline style rule in the markup.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner>kontrollen bruker et ytre tabell-beholder for bruk av innebygd stil regelen i koden.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.ChangePasswordDesigner>

trans-unit.source: You can remove the outer table container by setting this property to true.
trans-unit.target: Du kan fjerne beholderen ytre tabell ved å angi denne egenskapen til sann.

trans-unit.source: Removing the outer table gives you greater flexibility in how you apply CSS rules to the markup that is rendered by the control.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner tabellen ytre gir deg bedre fleksibilitet i hvordan du bruke CSS regler markup gjengis av kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control uses an outer table container to apply inline CSS style rules; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kontrollen bruker et ytre tabell-beholder til å bruke innebygd CSS-stilregler; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Sets the value of a template of the associated control.
trans-unit.target: Angir verdien for en mal for den tilknyttede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The SetEditableDesignerRegionContent method sets an editable region in a designer to a control or template that is specified in its persisted form by the `content` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden SetEditableDesignerRegionContent angir en redigerbare området i en designer til en kontroll eller en mal som er angitt i det faste skjemaet av den `content` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"></xref> to set content for.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.EditableDesignerRegion"> </xref> angi innhold for.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> containing a persisted control or template.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.String>som inneholder en fast kontroll eller malen.</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection of template groups for the templates of the control that is associated with this designer.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling av malen grupper for malene for kontrollen som er knyttet til utformeren.

trans-unit.source: The TemplateGroups property constructs a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection> object and populates it with the collection returned by the base property.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen sammensetningene TemplateGroups en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>objekt og tabellen fylles ut med samlingen ble returnert av egenskapen base.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection>

trans-unit.source: It then adds a <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup> object for each of the templates (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.ChangePasswordTemplate%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.SuccessTemplate%2A>) of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control.
trans-unit.target: Den deretter legger til en <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>objekt for hver av malene (<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.ChangePasswordTemplate%2A> og <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.SuccessTemplate%2A>) for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.SuccessTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword.ChangePasswordTemplate%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroup>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"></xref> containing an element for each template in the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.TemplateGroupCollection"> </xref> som inneholder et element for hver mal i den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control that is associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om designer må bruke en midlertidig kopi i stedet for den faktiske kontrollen som er forbundet med designer for å generere utformingen markup.

trans-unit.source: Because the UsePreviewControl property is always `true`, the designer uses a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control that contains a temporary copy of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> control to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Fordi egenskapen UsePreviewControl alltid `true`, designer bruker en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>kontroll som inneholder en midlertidig kopi av det tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>kontrollen til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View> control does not affect any persistence for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>Kontrollen påvirker ikke noen utholdenhet for <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.View>

trans-unit.source: If the UsePreviewControl property were overridden to return `false`, the designer would use the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword> itself to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Hvis egenskapen UsePreviewControl ble overstyrt for å returnere `false`, designer bruker den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>selve til å generere utformingen markup.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ChangePassword>

trans-unit.source: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Always <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
